<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFF8EFFD4FC91704EDD5DF982" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FF8EFFD4FC91704EDD5DF982" blockId="63.[792,1399,1385,1537]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF8EFFD4FC91704EDBF1FA02" bold="true" box="[794,905,1385,1409]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76">Comment</emphasis>
: The original description is based on 
<specimenCount id="E8C006A9FF8EFFD4FA9F704EDD0EFA01" box="[1300,1398,1385,1410]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" type="generic" typeStatus="type">nine type</specimenCount>
specimens from Danum Valley, 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FF8EFFD4FBE870AEDCDBFA22" box="[1123,1187,1417,1441]" country="Malaysia" name="Sabah" pageId="63" pageNumber="76">Sabah</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FF8EFFD4FB3A70AEDD5BFA22" author="PACE, R." box="[1201,1315,1417,1441]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" pagination="727 - 794" refId="ref78194" refString="PACE, R. 2014: Aleocharinae from Sabah (Borneo) collected by Guillaume de Rougemont (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 46 (1): 727 - 794." type="journal article" year="2014">PACE 2014</bibRefCitation>
). It does not seem unlikely that either this species or 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF8EFFD4FB6E708EDD19FA42" baseAuthorityName="Bernhauer" baseAuthorityYear="1911" box="[1253,1377,1449,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mirabilis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF8EFFD4FB6E708EDD19FA42" box="[1253,1377,1449,1473]" italics="true" pageId="63" pageNumber="76">O. mirabilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF8EFFD4FC5970EEDCA6FA62" authority="PACE, 2007" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2007" box="[978,1246,1481,1505]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="borneanus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF8EFFD4FC5970EEDC24FA62" box="[978,1116,1481,1505]" italics="true" pageId="63" pageNumber="76">O. borneanus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FF8EFFD4FBEF70EEDCA6FA62" author="PACE, R." box="[1124,1246,1481,1505]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" pagination="743 - 769" refId="ref77939" refString="PACE, R. 2007: Le specie del genere Orphnebius MOTSCHULSCKY [sic], 1858, nel Borneo (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 114 (4): 743 - 769." type="journal article" year="2007">PACE, 2007</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. The genitalia are quite similar (see figures in 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FF8EFFD4FBEC70CEDCA0F982" author="PACE, R." box="[1127,1240,1513,1537]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" pagination="743 - 769" refId="ref77939" refString="PACE, R. 2007: Le specie del genere Orphnebius MOTSCHULSCKY [sic], 1858, nel Borneo (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 114 (4): 743 - 769." type="journal article" year="2007">PACE 2007</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FF8EFFD4FB6970CEDD62F982" author="PACE, R." box="[1250,1306,1513,1537]" pageId="63" pageNumber="76" pagination="727 - 794" refId="ref78194" refString="PACE, R. 2014: Aleocharinae from Sabah (Borneo) collected by Guillaume de Rougemont (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 46 (1): 727 - 794." type="journal article" year="2014">2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
